Privacy Policy for ChatZone
Effective Date: July 25, 2025

Shaheen Tech ("we", "us", or "our") operates the mobile application ChatZone (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our App and services.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:

a. Personal Information
Name, email address, and phone number (for account creation or subscription)

Payment information (via secure third-party processors)

Referral data (when using referral program)

b. Usage Information
Chat history (used to improve user experience, not shared)

IP address and device details

Search queries and image generation logs

c. Cookies and Tracking
Analytics data to monitor usage patterns and improve functionality

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:

Provide and improve our GPT-powered chat and other AI tools

Process your subscriptions and payments

Enable the referral system

Offer customer support

Ensure security and prevent fraud

Comply with legal obligations

3. Sharing of Information
We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties, except:

Service Providers: For hosting, analytics, and payment processing

Legal Requirements: If required by law or governmental authority

Business Transfers: In case of merger or acquisition

4. Subscription & Payments
All payments are processed through secure third-party providers (e.g., Google Play Billing). We do not store any card or bank information on our servers.

5. Data Security
We implement strong security measures to protect your data, including:

SSL encryption

Secure cloud hosting

Regular audits

However, no method of transmission is 100% secure.

